+- Beautiful large hero header with dramatic title "SherpaCarta" and subtitle "A Magna Carta for the 21st Century".
+- Strong visual hierarchy with excellent spacing and typography (use serif fonts for the constitution text).
+- Clear "The Purpose" section with strong, inspiring text.
+- One large, prominent, fully editable main textarea for the full Living Constitution (make it tall, beautiful, with nice padding and focus states).
