+- Add a refined "Give A Bit • Support the Movement" section at the bottom with Bitcoin contribution feel.
+- Keep the Sherpa Oath modal but make it more elegant.
+- Overall feel: solemn, trustworthy, important, timeless, and premium. Avoid anything that looks cheap or basic.
+
+Improve layout, spacing, buttons, borders, shadows, and hover effects. Make the whole page feel like a serious constitutional document that commands respect.
+
+Output only the complete improved src/App.jsx file.

